  "title": "Quantity Surveyor",
  "description": "<p><br></p>\n<p>Job Description &amp; Requirements</p>\n<p>- Prepare and analyze cost comparison for tender submission</p>\n<p>- Responsible for measuring quantities and taking off</p>\n<p>- To process monthly progress claim and final claim</p>\n<p>- To attend to all relevant contracts administration and documentation for the project</p>\n<p>- To liaise with Consultants / Main Contractors on variation order and progress claim</p>\n<p>- To liaise with suppliers for quotations</p>\n<p>- To maintain relevant documentation in an orderly and proper manner</p>\n<p>- All other QS related job</p>\n<p>- Candidate must possess at least a Degree / Diploma in Building or its equivalent</p>\n<p>- Minimum 3 years of working experience in the related field is required for this position.</p>\n<p>- Required skills : MS Project, Autocad</p>\n<p>- Analytical, resourceful, independent, reponsibility and able to work in a challenging and fast paced environment.</p>\n<p>- Good interpersonal, communication and negotiation skills</p>\n<p>- Full-time positions</p>",
